## 12) Acceptance Criteria

### Home

* Home always shows an action path (no dead dashboards).
* Home suggestions are capped at 4 and are eligible/relevant.
* “Add service” entry is visible and consistent.

### Drawer

* Drawer opens from all required entry points.
* Recommendations are suppressed correctly based on NA categories and hide feedback.
* One-tap add works with Undo.
* Default level is selected and explainable.

### Suggestions

* Throttling prevents spam (no repeated suggestion loops).
* Hide feedback suppresses suggestions for the configured period.

### Routine

* Draft routine can be built without subscription (if enabled).
* Upgrade/adjacent add surfaces exist but are not cluttered.

