## 14) Opinionated Guidance (Do this, not that)

### Do

* Keep suggestions few and high-confidence.
* Make Home feel like a calm dashboard with gentle next steps.
* Make “Add” truly one-tap with defaults and Undo.
* Let users browse/draft before pay if you want higher conversion.

### Don’t

* Turn Home into a shopping feed.
* Show 10+ suggested services.
* Suggest services the home can’t possibly need.
* Force subscription before showing any value.

